<template>
    <v-carousel height="400" show-arrows="hover" cycle hide-delimiter-background>
        <v-carousel-item v-for="(slide, i) in slides" :key="i">
            <v-img :src="colors[i]" height="100%">

            </v-img>
        </v-carousel-item>
    </v-carousel>
</template>
<script>

import B1 from "../assets/Banners/"
export default {
    name: 'carouselComponent',

    data() {
        return {
            colors: [
                img1,
                img1, img1, img1, img1, img1, img1, img1, img1, img1,
            ],
            slides: [
                'First',
                'Second',
                'Third',
                'Fourth',
                'Fifth',
            ],
        }
    },
}
</script>
